        <div class="container">
            <div class="row g-5 align-items-center">
                <div class="col-lg-6" data-aos="fade-right">
                    <span class="text-uppercase fw-bold mb-3 d-block" style="color: var(--primary-yellow); letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 0.85rem;">Qatar's Top Cabin Manufacturers</span>
                    <h2 class="hero-title fw-bold mb-4" style="font-size: var(--fs-h2); line-height: 1.2; color: #fff; letter-spacing: -0.01em; text-transform:none;">High-Quality Porta Cabin Fabrication in Doha</h2>
                    <p class="mb-4" style="font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #aaa;">
                        Operating as a trusted <strong>portable cabin supplier in Qatar</strong>, BestChoice Contracting leads the industry in fabricating versatile, climate-proof modular structures. For over 15 years, our team has engineered specialized <a href="/porta-cabin-offices" style="color:#fff; text-decoration:none; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-yellow);">temporary site offices</a>, expansive <a href="/labor-camps-accommodation" style="color:#fff; text-decoration:none; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-yellow);">labor camp accommodations</a>, and secure <a href="/security-guard-cabins" style="color:#fff; text-decoration:none; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-yellow);">guard cabins</a> customized for the demanding environment of the Middle East.
                    </p>
                    <p style="line-height: 1.8; color: #aaa;">
                        We understand that every industrial, commercial, and oil &amp; gas project has specific footprint and regulatory requirements. Our robust <a href="/container-office-cabins" style="color:#fff; text-decoration:none; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-yellow);">shipping container modifications</a> and multi-storey prefab buildings are constructed with precision—integrating high-grade EPS/Rockwool insulation, rigorous structural steel frameworks, and premium epoxy finishing. Choose BestChoice Contracting for rapid, reliable, and compliant modular construction.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6" data-aos="fade-left">
                    <div class="row g-4">
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <div class="p-4 h-100" style="background:#111; border-left: 3px solid var(--primary-yellow);">
                                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3" style="font-size: 1.15rem; color: #fff;">In-House Manufacturing</h4>
                                <p class="small mb-0" style="line-height:1.7; color:#888;">Complete fabrication control at our Doha workshop, enabling strict quality assurance and fast turnaround.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <div class="p-4 h-100" style="background:#111; border-left: 3px solid var(--primary-yellow);">
                                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3" style="font-size: 1.15rem; color: #fff;">Custom Container Conversions</h4>
                                <p class="small mb-0" style="line-height:1.7; color:#888;">Expert modification of 20ft and 40ft containers into compliant, durable site workspaces and stores.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <div class="p-4 h-100" style="background:#111; border-left: 3px solid var(--primary-yellow);">
                                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3" style="font-size: 1.15rem; color: #fff;">Qatar Labour Law Compliant</h4>
                                <p class="small mb-0" style="line-height:1.7; color:#888;">All accommodation cabins and sanitary blocks exceed local municipal and worker welfare standards.</p>
                            </div>
